The paper deals with image processing and specifically with patch-based image models/priors. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of wavelet frames, which is a common technique in signal processing, suggesting that it could also belong to cs.SP (Signal Processing). The paper also discusses the use of optimization techniques, suggesting that it could belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper discusses the computational feasibility of the proposed method, suggesting that it could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
